### Repositorio para implementacao das rotas da Lumx no smart contract da Rivool Finance.

- Os contratos e ambiente sao para testes e entedimento das rotas da Lumx no smart contract.

```javascript
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/create-wallet \
-H "Content-Type: application/json"
```

```javascript
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/invest-usdc \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{
  "walletId": "53451fa8-6be6-47a1-926c-856354df3b19",
  "amount": 1000000
}'
```

```javascript
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/approve \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{
  "walletId": "c9ea91be-1cee-400c-8509-410cf3329605",
  "spender": "0xeef3dda161622e541416bd9dd46db82bb91c2a09",
  "value": 1000000
}'
```